      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n    \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"\"      alt\u003d\"App Icon\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003eOn-Shelf Availability Analytics App\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n      The On-Shelf Availability Analytics App helps retail managers proactively monitor, predict, and prevent out-of-stock situations across stores and products. It achieves this by combining inventory tracking, sales pattern analysis, and predictive modeling to optimize shelf availability and reduce phantom inventory.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Store and Product Data: Requires sales and inventory data for each product across all stores.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Safety Stock Levels: Utilizes defined safety stock thresholds to predict potential stockouts.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Sales and Inventory Visualizations: Provides charts on total sales over time, zero sales days per store or product, and total units sold.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Out-of-Stock and Phantom Inventory Alerts: Displays day-wise phantom inventory levels, possible out-of-stock situations based on safety stock breaches, and highlights consecutive zero sales days.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Key Insights: Reveals phantom inventory gaps, predicts stockouts from safety stock breaches, and identifies most and least-engaged stores.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eBenefits\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Proactive Stock Management: Predicts and prevents out-of-stock issues, ensuring product availability.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Reduced Phantom Inventory: Detects and addresses discrepancies for accurate inventory counts.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Optimized Shelf Availability: Maximizes sales opportunities by keeping shelves stocked.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Improved Customer Satisfaction: Enhances the shopping experience through consistent product availability.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Data-Driven Decisions: Provides actionable insights for informed inventory and replenishment strategies.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\u003csection\u003e\r\n  \u003ch4\u003eData Description\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"custom-table-container\"\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"custom-table-header\"\u003e\r\n      \u003ctable class\u003d\"custom-table\"\u003e\r\n        \u003cthead\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\r\n            \u003cth\u003eField Name\u003c/th\u003e\r\n            \u003cth\u003eDescription\u003c/th\u003e\r\n          \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n        \u003c/thead\u003e\r\n      \u003c/table\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"custom-table-body\"\u003e\r\n      \u003ctable class\u003d\"custom-table\"\u003e\r\n        \u003ctbody\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003estore_id\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eStore identifier.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003esku\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eProduct identifier.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003edate\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eTransaction date.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003etotal_sales_units\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eDaily unit sales.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003ezero_sales_flag\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eNo sales indicator (0/1).\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eproduct_category\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eProduct group.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003edaily_sales_units\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eAverage daily sales.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eoos_alert\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eStock-out risk flag (0/1).\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003ephantom_inventory\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eInventory discrepancy.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003ephantom_inventory_ind\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eDiscrepancy flag (0/1).\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n        \u003c/tbody\u003e\r\n      \u003c/table\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/section\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n",
